column1: #text=I like to cook a lot but I am not a very good baker .
#text=So I never bake cakes from scratch .
#text=However I do like cake al ot so I do bake them .
#text=They are easy to use and make a very nice cake .
#text=it really does n't take much time .
#text=All you need to do is get one bowl .
#text=Add the cake mix from the box .
#text=Either 2 or 3 eggs added to the bowl .
#text=Then a half cup of oil and finally about a cup of water .
#text=Then you need to get your mixer and put it on medium and mix it all up for 2 to 3 minutes .
#text=Then put it into a non stick cake pan and bake for about 30 minutes .
#text=So all together about 10 minutes preparation and 30 minutes baking you can have a good tasting cake in 40 minutes .
#text=I do n't really like frosting so as soon as it cools I cut myself a slice .
